{{version031}}
{{flavour|Hurls an exploding ball of negative energy which drains any living creature it engulfs.}}

'''Ghostly Fireball''' is a monster-only spell which behaves much like the [[Fireball]] spell, dealing heavy, unavoidable damage to everything caught in its 3Ã—3 blast radius. Unlike Fireball, however, it deals pure [[negative energy]] damage.

{{monsters with spell}}

Additionally, a {{monsterlink|Blood saint}}'s [[Legendary Destruction]] spell can result in a ghostly fireball.

==History==
*Prior to [[0.19]], this spell dealt partially-irrestistable [[negative energy]] damage and healed any [[undead]] affected by it.
*Prior to [[0.17]], Ghostly Fireball's damage partially bypassed AC.
*Ghostly Fireball was added in [[0.13]].

